How can you be so rude to a lady?

201
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:28,940
你叫什么名字？…
What is your name? What is your name?

202
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:32,350
你叫什么名字？
What is your name? What is your name?

203
00:20:33,320 --> 00:20:34,380
WHAT IS YOUR NAME？
What is your name

204
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:36,670
意思是怎样用中文称呼你？
Means what's your name in Chinese!

205
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,590
你叫什么名字？
What is your name?

206
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:41,430
师傅，我天天吃豆我天天拉肚子
Master, I've been eating too many beans,

207
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:44,790
如果再没有饭吃，我也快将没命！
if I don't have rice soon, I'll die too.

208
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:51,870
小心！红蕃冲着我们来了！
Watch out! The Red Hair's coming.

209
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:15,110
对不起，对不起…
I beg your pardon.

210
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:28,190
黄飞鸿…黄师傅…
Wong Fai-hong. Master Wong.

211
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,620
十三姨
Aunt Yee.

212
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:33,750
十三姨，喝杯茶
Aunt Yee, would you like a cup of tea?

213
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:37,190
黄师傅！
Master Wong.

214
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,150
黄飞鸿！
Wong Fai-hong.

215
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:42,790
师傅的伞？
This is Master's umbrella!

216
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:45,030
十三姨，十三姨…
Aunt Yee...

217
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,390
看，是师傅的伞！
Look, this is Master's umbrella.

218
00:21:49,560 --> 00:21:52,350
十三姨呀，我们吃完午餐再找吧！
Aunt Yee, shall we have lunch first?

219
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:54,030
我不饿，你们先吃吧！
I ain't hungry. You guys go ahead.

220
00:21:57,280 --> 00:22:00,150
你们这些中国人到这里来干什么？
What are you Chinese doing here?

221
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:03,270
我们在找一位朋友，他在上游遇到意外
We are looking for a friend..He had an accident up river.

222
00:22:03,520 --> 00:22:04,870
你该知道巴利镇长不喜欢…
Now you know Mayor Barclly...

223
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:08,390
看见中国人擅自离开应有范围
doesn't wanna see you Chinese outside your alley.

224
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:12,990
你就通融当作没见过我们吧！
Would you just pretend you did not see us?

225
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:16,030
怒难从命
Sorry. No, I can't do.

226
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:19,070
死洋鬼子！我们找人都不行呀？
You bastard, we are only searching for our friend.

227
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:20,990
他们老是把我们华人矿工不当人
They treat us Chinese miners like dogs,

228
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,150
我们都习惯
having all kinds of restrictions on us.

229
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:24,630
可是他们老是欺负我们
Yeah! We are always on the wrong side.

230
00:22:24,840 --> 00:22:27,190
这里只有他一个人，把他干掉
Shall we stand together and overcome him now?

231
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:32,270
不不…警长对我们中国人算不错了
No... The sergeant is nice to us Chinese indeed!

232
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:33,550
你不记得嘛？
Remember?

233
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:37,540
有几次他把欺负我们的洋鬼子赶走呀！
He had driven away.some white bastards for us several times.

234
00:22:37,760 --> 00:22:39,270
走呀，走呀！
Let's go!

235
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:41,310
喂
Hey!

236
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:42,390
什么
Yes?

237
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:46,710
记住，这儿绝不容许中国女人前来
Remember, no Chinese women allowed here.

238
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,670
此乃本地法例
That's the law.

239
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:50,830
我会记住的了
I will not forget.

240
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:57,950
“林肯”先生，后会有期
Goodbye, Mr Lincoln.

241
00:23:03,800 --> 00:23:07,990
你别袒心，黄飞鸿定必吉人天相
Don't worry Ma'am. Wong Fei-hong.is gonna be just fine.

242
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:10,590
喂！你在干嘛？
Hey! What are you doing here?

243
00:23:10,800 --> 00:23:12,510
再动手动脚，就对你不客气
Behave yourself or I won't give you face.

244
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:13,270
什么
What?

245
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:14,870
“WHAT”你的妈！
"What"? The hell!

246
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:21,880
“WHAT你的妈”！我喜欢呀！
What the hell? I like that.

247
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:03,590
十三姨，雨下得很大，进去吧
It's raining dogs and cats, please go back inside.

248
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:08,710
不行！我怕飞鸿回来找不到门口
No, Fai-hong won't find us when he is back.

249
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:14,150
如果你冷病了，师傅会很心痛
Master would be upset if you fell sick.

250
00:24:14,280 --> 00:24:17,190
对，十三姨，进去吧
Exactly, please go back inside.

251
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:38,300
让开…
Give way...

252
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:39,630
你们看什么？
What are you guys looking at?

253
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:40,350
看女人呀
It is a woman.

254
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:41,710
女人有什么好看？
What's so excited about a woman?

255
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:44,590
汉叔，你这么老，还看？
Uncle Han, don't you think.you're too old for that?

256
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:47,360
我不能做点什么，但看看总可以吧
But I can still see well with my eyes.

257
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:50,190
走吧！走吧！今天不开门呀！
Shoot! We are closed for business today.

258
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:51,710
十三姨
Aunt Yee!

259
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:54,350
阿七，帮我试试够不够黏
Seven, help me to check its texture.

260
00:25:54,360 --> 00:25:54,910
是！
Yes!

261
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:56,870
看要不要加点水？
Should I add more water?

262
00:25:58,280 --> 00:26:00,630
好…
Good!... Good!...

263
00:26:15,080 --> 00:26:17,430
阿苏，你在吃什么？
Sol, what are you eating?

264
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:20,710
那是浆糊！
This is glue.

265
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:22,750
黏不黏呀？
Is it sticky enough?

266
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:24,510
黏呀，黏呀
Very!

267
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,910
你…你又说“GOOD”！
And you! Why did you say it tastes good?

268
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:31,270
我没说，我只是点头而已
I did not! I was only nodding.

269
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:33,950
你们帮我拿些寻人启事到街上去贴
Go post these Lost and Found bills on the street.

270
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:35,380
啊！
Yes Ma'am.

271
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:38,150
你拿浆糊吧
Let's go, gluey-mouth.

272
00:26:52,320 --> 00:26:53,380
这里贴一张
Post one here.

273
00:27:03,120 --> 00:27:04,260
这里也贴一张
Post one here!

274
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:18,350
喂，你们在做什么？
Hey! What the hell you boys.think you're doing here?

275
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:20,430
你们为什么把我们的寻人启示撕掉？
Why did you tear our poster away?

276
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:22,270
我们在找师傅
We're looking for our master!

277
00:27:22,560 --> 00:27:24,390
你们不能在这儿贴告示
You can't hang those posters here!

278
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:25,540
他到底说什么？
What did he say?

279
00:27:25,760 --> 00:27:29,510
没…没什么！走吧！走吧！
Nothing... Let's go.

280
00:27:31,040 --> 00:27:33,990
再贴便把你俩收监！
You hang one more poster, you're going to jail.

281
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:45,740
副队长
Deputy!

282
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:02,860
妈的！
Damn!

283
00:28:03,080 --> 00:28:04,430
那些钱呀！
The money.

284
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,390
你身手都不错呀
Hey, you are good.

285
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,670
过奖过奖
Thanks partner,

286
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:41,390
你何时教我“WHAT你的妈”呀？
when are you going to teach me.some of "What your mother"?

287
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:42,310
什么？
What?

288
00:28:42,560 --> 00:28:43,780
这个哩
This!

289
00:28:46,320 --> 00:28:47,590
可以教我吗？
Can you show me?

290
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:50,550
你想练腿功呀？
You want to learn leg stance?

291
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:52,870
不怕辛苦就成了！
If not you can put up with the hardship.

292
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:53,870
像我这样！
Like this!

293
00:28:54,080 --> 00:28:56,590
每天压腿两个时辰！
Press each of your legs like this for 4 hours.

294
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:58,630
那就成了！
That's all it takes.

295
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:01,270
好的
Alright.

296
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:03,270
小子，你们被捕了
OK boys, you're under arrest,

297
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:04,550
监狱就在那边
the jail's that way.

298
00:29:04,760 --> 00:29:07,950
放心，一切已在我控制之中
Take it easy partner..I've got everything under control.

299
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,710
走吧
Yeah, move it.

300
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:11,350
好的，来吧
Alright come on.

301
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:14,190
请问阁下高姓大名？
What do they call you son?

302
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,540
我叫比利
My name is Billy!

303
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:18,590
比利，你可有兴趣做我的副手？
Billy, interested in being my deputy?

304
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:21,510
让我拿到奖金才说吧
We'll talk after I get my reward.

305
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:23,790
NICK
Nick

306
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:25,310
数完了没有？
You done yet?

307
00:29:25,560 --> 00:29:26,830
真讨厌！
God damn Sheriff

308
00:29:27,040 --> 00:29:32,030
给你吵一吵我又要从头再数了！
you made me lose my count..Now I have to start all over again.

309
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:33,630
警长，出手太低了吧？
Sheriff, the pay is bad.

310
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:35,310
工作又缠身
I've to cut partial of my freedom.

311
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:37,190
我明白了
I understand!

312
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:40,630
你大可在我有困难时才前来解围
You can come to work with me.only when there is a trouble.

313
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:44,510
一言为定
Sheriff, you got yourself a deputy.

314
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:48,590
那么…试试这个吧
Good, try this on for size.

315
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:09,710
如碰见到这个男人，请来诊所通知我们
Hi, if you see this man, we're at the clinic.

316
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:14,390
如碰见到这个男人，请来诊所通知我们
If you see this man, we're at the clinic.

317
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:18,070
赏面喝一杯吗？
How about a drink?

318
00:30:18,280 --> 00:30:19,500
恕我失陪
No, thank you.

319
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:23,110
我要你喝
When I say drink,

320
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,630
你便要喝
you drink.

321
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:27,190
放开她
Hey! Leave her alone.

322
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,590
住口
You shut up.

323
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:41,310
再来一个
Have another.

324
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:51,790
好标致的中国娃娃啊！
You are a pretty China doll.

325
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,630
你走那么快干什么？
Hey lady where are you going?

326
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,630
你要是不喝
If you don't want to drink.

327
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:00,110
只好照头淋了
Then wear it!

328
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:03,630
不要！住手！
Stop it stop it stop it...

329
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:12,390
十三姨…十三姨
Aunt Yee! Aunt Yee.

330
00:31:21,840 --> 00:31:25,430
若我是你们，便绝不这般无聊
Now all the boys,.I wouldn't do that if I were you,

331
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:33,910
你想打架，在下乐意奉陪
you wanna fight, well, you've got one.

332
00:31:43,760 --> 00:31:45,790
我不是要生事
I aint looking for no fight.

333
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:47,140
太好了！
That's good.

334
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:50,710
我不服气，阿七，帮我教训他们
Now I want a fight! Seven, teach them a lesson.

335
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,780
好
Sure!

336
00:31:54,600 --> 00:31:56,830
我们不如试点新意
Why don't we try something different, pal?

337
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,870
来一场友谊赛怎么样？
Care for a friendly wager?

338
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:03,750
我赌这个中国人不用枪便可把你击倒
Now I bet this Chinamen can wipe you.out without your guns.

339
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,790
我将赌注全押在他身上
And my money is on the Chinamen, pal

340
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:08,030
你们哪个先上？
which one is man enough to fight him?

341
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:34,710
我赢了！
I win!

342
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:37,710
不行！趁师傅不在，要打个够
No, this is only good for a warm up.since master isn't around.

343
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:38,780
阿苏，翻译
Sol, translate for me.

344
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:39,670
什么？
What?

345
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:41,100
叫他们全部一起上
Tell them to fight me all at once.

346
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:43,350
如果都能打赢我的，都算他们赢！
They are the winner if anyone of them beat me.

347
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:44,790
他说什么？
What did he say?

348
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:47,670
他叫你们一起上
He said he wants to fight you all.

349
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:49,670
如果你们赢了，钱就归你们
If you win, you can keep the money.

350
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:51,870
全都一起上？且’慢
All? Wait a minute,

351
00:32:52,080 --> 00:32:53,750
我们会输的
we might lose!

352
00:32:53,760 --> 00:32:55,870
阿七，他说你如…
Seven, he said if...

353
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:56,990
相信我
Trust me.

354
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,420
相信我
Trust me.

355
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,910
对不起！相信他才是
Sorry! Trust him!

356
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,150
乐死我了！
I am a happy man.

357
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:45,300
我也是！
Me too.

358
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,790
十三姨，你呢？
Aunt Yee, what about you?

359
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:47,750
我也一样
Me too.

360
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,670
谢谢！
Thank you!

361
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:03,780
我现在那有心情看风景呀
How can I enjoy this beautiful landscape now?

362
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:06,950
不如你带我去你们找到我的那个地方
Why don't you take me back to where you found me?

363
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:09,620
也许我会想起我是从那里来的
Maybe I can remember where I come from.

364
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:13,670
不过你都不知道我在讲什么
Only you have no idea on what I am saying.

365
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:22,790
衣服，你要是会说话就好了
Clothes, how I wish you could talk.

366
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:25,830
你可以告诉我，我到底是谁呀？
Then you would be able to explain everything.

367
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:44,150
师傅…金山…开宝芝林…一周年…
Master... America... Setting up Po Chi Lam....One year anniversary,

368
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,790
牙擦…
Sol...

369
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:50,430
这封信是我写给别人的
What's this letter about?

370
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:53,310
还是别人写给我的呢？
Is it by me or for me?

371
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:58,190
难道我叫牙擦
My name is Sol?

372
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:02,830
师傅？！我有个师傅
... and I have a master?

373
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:06,900
那我找到他，我就什么都知道了
I must find him, he will have the answer.

374
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:10,670
黄飞！
Wong Fai!

375
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:13,950
我一定认识他
I must have known him.

376
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:18,350
如果找到他我就知道我是谁了
If I found him, everything would be explained.

377
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:45,390
有何贵干？
What can I do for you?

378
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:50,870
我要娶你的女儿
I want to marry your daughter!

379
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:53,070
你岂敢侮辱我妹妹？
How dare you insult my sister?

380
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:58,350
你们是最弱的部落
You are the weakest among all the tribes,

381
00:35:58,600 --> 00:36:01,160
若你拒绝将女儿嫁我，我就灭你全族
if you don't give me your daughter,.I will destory you all.

382
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:06,030
战鹰
Fierce Eagle!

383
00:36:08,160 --> 00:36:11,510
我们不怕你，我们会战斗到底
We are not afraid of you,.we will fight you to death!

384
00:36:21,200 --> 00:36:22,750
战鹰
Fierce Eagle!

385
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:37,830
请不要动手
Please, do not fight!

386
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,910
喂，不要
Hey, don't...

387
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:44,950
阿黄，别跟他打
Yellow, please do not fight him.

388
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:02,790
喂…
Hey...

389
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,990
来吧！
Come on!

390
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:09,110
让我试试看！
Let me try.

391
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,550
你想怎样？
What are you doing?

392
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:24,950
住手！
Stop it. Don't!

393
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:35,980
咦！痊愈了
I'm good, I'm good...

