01:10:39,720 --> 01:10:42,100
还用你指点？
You don't tell me what I can and can't do, Billy!

762
01:10:42,120 --> 01:10:44,110
别闹了，比利
Now settle down son.

763
01:10:44,560 --> 01:10:47,310
案发时我跟阿七和阿苏在一起
Look, I was with Doc Sol and Seven.right before the hold-up.

764
01:10:47,560 --> 01:10:48,700
他们是被诬陷的！
They've been framed.

765
01:10:48,920 --> 01:10:51,630
我不管你有什么理由
I don't give a damn if you come up.with a hundred reasons.

766
01:10:51,880 --> 01:10:54,910
我们在宝芝林发现赃款，证据确凿
The fact is we found some of the stolen money.in Po Chi Lam.

767
01:10:56,560 --> 01:10:58,150
不是中国人抢劫，还有谁？
If the Chinamen didn't take the money, who did?

768
01:10:58,360 --> 01:10:59,910
我呀？
Me?

769
01:11:01,120 --> 01:11:02,510
也许是比利你
Maybe it was you Billy!

770
01:11:02,720 --> 01:11:05,510
神经病！我还击中其中一个劫匪哩
No! That's crazy! I shot one of'em.

771
01:11:05,720 --> 01:11:07,310
也许你想灭口！
Maybe you were trying to throw us off.

772
01:11:07,560 --> 01:11:09,510
说不定你正是贼人同党
Maybe you're working with the gang.

773
01:11:11,680 --> 01:11:13,150
比利，别乱来
Easy there, Billy.

774
01:11:15,400 --> 01:11:16,990
别轻举妄动
I wont let you do it.

775
01:11:17,200 --> 01:11:18,590
你阻止得了吗？
How are you going to stop me?

776
01:11:18,800 --> 01:11:19,990
我杀了你
I'll kill you.

777
01:11:33,400 --> 01:11:34,910
你没事吧？
Are you alright?

778
01:11:35,560 --> 01:11:37,390
没想到他们先下手为强
I guess someone was quicker at that time.

779
01:11:37,680 --> 01:11:39,350
你是中国人的真正朋友
You're a real friend to the Chinese.

780
01:11:39,800 --> 01:11:42,910
比利，I 欣赏你 T00
Billy! I appreciate you too!

781
01:11:50,640 --> 01:11:54,030
安静！听我说几句话
Settle down. I said settle down.

782
01:12:02,880 --> 01:12:05,550
他说他帮我们争取最好的条件
He said he would get the best deal for us,

783
01:12:08,040 --> 01:12:10,500
只要我们交出七个人认罪
provided that 7 of us would confess to the crime,

784
01:12:11,120 --> 01:12:13,190
我们认了罪要判囚多久？
If we confess, do we go jail?

785
01:12:13,200 --> 01:12:14,550
不会判囚
You can forget jail,

786
01:12:14,760 --> 01:12:16,110
你们只会被问吊
they are going to hang you.

787
01:12:17,120 --> 01:12:20,110
如你不认罪，所有人都要被问吊
If you don't confress to the crime,.they're going to hang you all.

788
01:12:20,320 --> 01:12:23,550
记住，赃款在你们中国人的地方找到
Remember, they found the money with you Chinese.

789
01:12:23,760 --> 01:12:26,110
不！不关所有中国人的事
No, not all the Chinese,

790
01:12:26,320 --> 01:12:28,150
只关宝芝林的人的事嘛
only the Po Chi Lam people.

791
01:12:28,760 --> 01:12:29,430
你说对不对
Am i right?

792
01:12:29,680 --> 01:12:31,630
不关我们事的，黄师傅！
Master Wong, non of my business

793
01:12:34,120 --> 01:12:35,710
龙叔说得对
Uncle Lone is right.

794
01:12:36,040 --> 01:12:39,150
这件事的确是宝芝林的事，与其他人无关
This is Po Chi Lam's problem,.nothing to do with you all.

795
01:12:39,360 --> 01:12:41,660
阿苏，你跟警长说
Sol, tell the sergeant,

796
01:12:41,960 --> 01:12:43,350
我一个人担当行不行？
can I take all the responsibility?

797
01:12:45,080 --> 01:12:46,140
不行！
No!

798
01:12:46,440 --> 01:12:49,980
师傅，不要说你一个人担当
You can't confess to the crime alone.

799
01:12:50,200 --> 01:12:51,990
就算师傅你认第一个
If you are going to be the first to confess,

800
01:12:52,200 --> 01:12:53,070
我阿苏就认第二个
I'll be the second.

801
01:12:53,280 --> 01:12:53,830
阿苏！
Sol!

802
01:12:54,040 --> 01:12:55,670
师傅，我叫阿七
Master, my nick name is Seven,

803
01:12:55,880 --> 01:12:58,510
我不是第三个，也是第七个！
if I am not the 3rd one, I will be the 7th one.

804
01:12:59,240 --> 01:13:00,300
飞鸿
Fai-hong.

805
01:13:00,720 --> 01:13:02,590
你们都别去，让我一个人来认
You all stay here, I'll go alone.

806
01:13:02,800 --> 01:13:04,070
这次分明是冤狱
This is a set up!

807
01:13:04,320 --> 01:13:07,670
黄师傅，你年青有为，一代宗师
Master Wong, you are young and capable.

808
01:13:07,880 --> 01:13:09,150
应该留着宝贵的生命
Your life should be...

809
01:13:09,160 --> 01:13:11,350
来帮我们华工做点事情
spared for the good of we Chinese workers.

810
01:13:11,600 --> 01:13:14,190
阿汉！你不是宝芝林的人
You've nothing to do with Po Chi Lam,

811
01:13:14,400 --> 01:13:16,430
不要多管闲事吧
don't get yourself into trouble!

812
01:13:16,680 --> 01:13:19,870
大叔！我们不是写华工血泪史
Uncle, we are not telling others.the pathetic tales of the Chinese workers.

813
01:13:20,120 --> 01:13:23,270
要写也是写华工光辉史
We want to tell the glorious history.of the Chinese workers.

814
01:13:25,040 --> 01:13:27,310
我黄飞鸿就一定要站出来
I, Wong Fai-hong, should stand for all of you.

815
01:13:27,440 --> 01:13:28,990
谁不同意？
Who disagrees?

816
01:13:29,240 --> 01:13:30,830
来吧！
Come with me.

817
01:13:40,520 --> 01:13:42,190
小姐，我去
Ma'am!

818
01:13:48,960 --> 01:13:50,230
飞鸿！
Fai-hong.

819
01:15:06,640 --> 01:15:08,270
都…都是我闯的祸
It's my fault!

820
01:15:09,240 --> 01:15:15,190
想不到一年前来美国开宝芝林分店
I couldn't imagine that, the establishment.of Po Chi Lam in the America a year ago,

821
01:15:16,200 --> 01:15:19,230
原来是为了这场浩劫铺路
would pave the way for tragedy.

822
01:15:20,240 --> 01:15:22,230
还…连累了师傅你！
And I dragged Master down too...

823
01:15:22,880 --> 01:15:25,230
汉叔！你怕不怕？
Uncle Han, are you afraid?

824
01:15:27,680 --> 01:15:32,270
讨老婆生子，勤做工讨吃
Getting married and working hard,

825
01:15:33,080 --> 01:15:37,150
在家扮皇帝，在外做奴隶
pretending as emperor at home.but working as slave outside...

826
01:15:39,040 --> 01:15:40,260
这样就一辈子了
That is my life!

827
01:15:43,280 --> 01:15:49,380
我们中国人的传统是死也要做只饱鬼
Sir, it is our custom,.man would die with a full stomach.

828
01:15:49,400 --> 01:15:51,150
请问我可以喂饱他们么？
May I feed them?

829
01:15:59,520 --> 01:16:02,630
死囚临死时会享用最后一顿饱饭
All the prisoners get their final meal.before they're executed.

830
01:16:02,880 --> 01:16:04,310
也不妨吧
What can it hurt?

831
01:16:18,640 --> 01:16:19,950
黄师傅
Master Wong.

832
01:16:22,120 --> 01:16:25,510
我能做的…就只有这一点
This is all I can do.

833
01:16:32,360 --> 01:16:35,980
黄师傅，有馅的
Master Wong, stuffed dumplings for you.

834
01:16:36,880 --> 01:16:38,390
吃吧！
Eat!

835
01:16:54,560 --> 01:16:57,510
师傅，靠你啦
Master, we all depend on you.

836
01:16:57,720 --> 01:16:59,910
师傅，我对你有信心
Master, I have full confidence in you.

837
01:17:05,320 --> 01:17:07,430
喂，再来一个呀
I want more!

838
01:17:14,560 --> 01:17:16,270
还有其他人没吃
They're waiting!

839
01:17:28,400 --> 01:17:29,150


840
01:17:29,400 --> 01:17:30,430


841
01:17:46,560 --> 01:17:50,230
为什么我们全给抓进去，你没有呢？
Why were you not in jail with us?

842
01:17:51,280 --> 01:17:52,670
我没有做什么事情
I didn't do anything.

843
01:17:53,920 --> 01:17:56,270
我没有…你错了！
I didn't do anything wrong.

844
01:18:00,200 --> 01:18:01,550
各位市民
Citizens,

845
01:18:02,840 --> 01:18:06,070
本人以镇长身分及因上帝之名
as Mayor of this town and in the name of God.

846
01:18:06,440 --> 01:18:11,300
在此见证一场公平的问吊
I'm here to witness this fair.and just execution of these men.

847
01:18:11,560 --> 01:18:14,070
上帝决定了他们行刑之日期
God has decided the day they are to die.

848
01:18:14,520 --> 01:18:17,550
而我就决定行刑的时辰
Now I shall decide their hour.

849
01:18:44,560 --> 01:18:45,190
闪开
Escape!

850
01:18:45,400 --> 01:18:46,990
大家躲开呀！
Move everyone.

851
01:20:23,400 --> 01:20:26,070
黄师傅，他们就是银行劫匪！
Master Wong, that's the robber.

852
01:20:26,280 --> 01:20:30,230
师傅，他是打劫银行的人
Master, he was the bank robber.

853
01:20:31,200 --> 01:20:33,630
我一定要抓住他，还我清白
I have to get him to clear my name.

854
01:20:34,040 --> 01:20:35,990
阿苏，先去救其他人
Sol, save the others first.

855
01:21:42,000 --> 01:21:43,670
师傅，这两个交给我！
Master, leave these two to me.

856
01:21:49,400 --> 01:21:50,790
镇长
Mayor Barcly.

857
01:21:53,920 --> 01:21:55,350
你来干什么？
What're the hell you're doing here?

858
01:21:55,600 --> 01:21:57,070
我想拿取我应得的余款
I need the rest of my money.

859
01:21:58,560 --> 01:22:00,670
其他中国人都怀疑我
The other Chinese is suspicious of me.

860
01:22:01,040 --> 01:22:02,350
我要离开本镇
I think I should leave town.

861
01:22:02,720 --> 01:22:05,670
你应该要离开本镇
You should leave town.

862
01:22:19,960 --> 01:22:21,350
你想怎样？
What do you want?

863
01:22:22,120 --> 01:22:23,750
我只限于跟你做交易！
I'm just doing business with you.

864
01:22:23,760 --> 01:22:26,060
我要取回我们那四十万元
I want my four hundred thousand.

865
01:22:26,760 --> 01:22:28,030
那是劫银行的赃款
That's the bank's money.

866
01:22:28,880 --> 01:22:31,390
你讲过一切易如反掌
You told me the job was gonna a cake walk,

867
01:22:31,680 --> 01:22:33,230
我有一个兄弟死了
but one of my man's been killed.

868
01:22:34,320 --> 01:22:36,990
对不起，这不关我的事
Sorry, I've nothing to do with that.

869
01:22:37,240 --> 01:22:38,590
这是意外
It was an accident.

870
01:22:39,600 --> 01:22:40,740
我也抱歉
I'm sorry too.

871
01:23:02,000 --> 01:23:03,870
妈的！
Damn it!

872
01:23:12,600 --> 01:23:13,870
去死吧
Go to hell.

873
01:23:21,240 --> 01:23:22,790
他妈的！
What the hell!

874
01:23:38,320 --> 01:23:41,940
小子！你是怎么走过来的？
You little bastard, how did you get there?

875
01:24:03,240 --> 01:24:04,550
妈的！
Shit!

876
01:24:04,920 --> 01:24:07,030
他是人是鬼！
What kind of a man is he?!

877
01:25:13,720 --> 01:25:14,550
给你
This is for you!

878
01:25:42,120 --> 01:25:43,750
打得够劲
Plays rough!

879
01:25:43,840 --> 01:25:45,910
正合我意
I like that.

880
01:26:23,920 --> 01:26:25,510
够狠不够？
You like that.

881
01:26:25,720 --> 01:26:26,940
算得什么？
I don't think so.

882
01:27:31,080 --> 01:27:32,190
来吧！
Come on!

883
01:29:19,680 --> 01:29:21,980
你在哪？
Where are you

884
01:29:24,160 --> 01:29:26,790
你在哪？
Where are you

885
01:29:37,160 --> 01:29:41,950
快出来，我们谈谈吧！
Come on out now, let's talk about it

886
01:31:06,520 --> 01:31:08,070
还不束手就擒？
Surrender now!

887
01:31:12,080 --> 01:31:12,830
还来？
You still fight?

888
01:31:49,920 --> 01:31:52,790
你是什么来的？
What the hell are you?

889
01:32:11,680 --> 01:32:12,710
抓紧
Hold it tight!

890
01:32:13,880 --> 01:32:15,100
放开我
Get off me

891
01:32:15,320 --> 01:32:16,750
我不需要你的帮忙
I don't need your help

892
01:32:17,440 --> 01:32:19,430
上来，危险！
Come on up. Look out!

893
01:32:40,440 --> 01:32:42,390
我要你来证明我的清白
I need you to prove my innocence.

894
01:32:45,120 --> 01:32:46,830
你简直不是人
You're not a human.

895
01:32:47,440 --> 01:32:48,710
起来吧
Get up!

896
01:33:02,680 --> 01:33:03,590
你怎么了？
Are you alright?

897
01:33:03,800 --> 01:33:05,430
你们怎么来的？
Why are you guys here?

898
01:33:05,880 --> 01:33:07,020
十三姨
Oh, Diana!

899
01:33:20,280 --> 01:33:21,830
飞鸿，你没事吧？
Fai-hong, are you alright?

900
01:33:22,040 --> 01:33:23,180
少筠你去那儿？
Where do you go?

901
01:33:23,520 --> 01:33:24,430
我找他们来救你呀
I get them here to help you!

902
01:33:24,680 --> 01:33:25,740
他们？谁是他们？
Who are they?

903
01:33:25,960 --> 01:33:26,940
他们是…
不要说了
- They are....- Forget it

904
01:33:27,160 --> 01:33:29,270
很多人受伤，我们先去救他们吧！
People are hurt. Let's go help them.

905
01:33:59,360 --> 01:34:00,670
阿七，准备采青
Seven, get ready for lion dance.

906
01:34:29,600 --> 01:34:30,580
来这里！
Come here!

907
01:34:44,160 --> 01:34:45,350
恭喜你比利
Congratulations, Billy.

908
01:34:45,440 --> 01:34:47,510
我相信你定会是一个好镇长
I trust you will be a good Mayor.

909
01:34:48,040 --> 01:34:49,020
作为新镇长
As a new Mayor,

910
01:34:49,240 --> 01:34:52,550
我以双方的友谊及了解作出声明
I proclaim in name of friendship and understanding

911
01:34:52,560 --> 01:34:57,190
由今天起这儿命名为唐人街
that from this day on, this area of Fort Stockton.will be known as China Town.

912
01:35:01,640 --> 01:35:03,990
我相信你一定像林肯一样，是个好领导人
I know you will be a good leader,.like Lincoln.

913
01:35:08,600 --> 01:35:09,430
阿黄，保重
Farewell, Yellow.

914
01:35:09,840 --> 01:35:10,900
我不是阿黄
I'm not Yellow.

915
01:35:11,640 --> 01:35:13,230
我叫黄飞鸿
My name is Wong Fai-hong.

916
01:35:13,440 --> 01:35:14,790
名字不重要
A name is just a name.

917
01:35:15,560 --> 01:35:17,430
你永远是我们的好兄弟
You'll always be our brother.

918
01:35:28,960 --> 01:35:30,020
他们是谁呀？
Who are they?

919
01:35:30,800 --> 01:35:32,230
你不记得他们了？
Don't you remember them?

920
01:35:39,840 --> 01:35:41,060
走吧
Come on!

921
01:35:44,680 --> 01:35:45,110
各位！
Everyone...

922
01:35:45,320 --> 01:35:46,950
黄师傅，不要再讲话了
Master Wong, no more speeches!

923
01:35:47,160 --> 01:35:48,380
是时候上车了吧
It's time to get going.

924
01:35:48,640 --> 01:35:51,550
对，你赶不上这班车，就赶不及那班船了
That's right, if you miss this train,.you'll miss the boat as well.

925
01:35:51,560 --> 01:35:52,590
你们快上路吧
Now go.

926
01:35:52,600 --> 01:35:53,990
是呀！是呀！
Yeah...

927
01:35:55,400 --> 01:35:56,510
阿七！
Seven!

928
01:35:57,080 --> 01:35:59,710
师傅，你不是准备了好多东西要讲的呀？
Master, didn't you have a long speech readied?

929
01:35:59,920 --> 01:36:01,110
这么快讲完了？
How come you finish your speech so soon?

930
01:36:05,640 --> 01:36:06,230
各位…
Everyone...

931
01:36:06,440 --> 01:36:07,830
黄师傅，不要再说了，请吧！
Master Wong, please do go now.

932
01:36:08,040 --> 01:36:10,030
上车吧
请上车吧！
- Get on the train..- Let's go!

933
01:36:10,240 --> 01:36:11,990
再见了
再见
- See you!.- See you...

934
01:36:14,560 --> 01:36:15,830
她到了！
Here she is!

935
01:36:16,840 --> 01:36:18,990
黄师傅，你多多保重呀
Master Wong, take care.

936
01:36:20,080 --> 01:36:21,670
你好吗？
How are you doing?

937
01:36:23,440 --> 01:36:24,950
那个女人是谁呀？
Who is that woman?

938
01:36:27,600 --> 01:36:29,310
听说是龙叔的老婆
People say she's Uncle Lone's wife.

939
01:36:29,680 --> 01:36:30,590
这里是什么鬼地方？
Where the hell is it?

940
01:36:30,600 --> 01:36:31,390
这么远啊
It's far from home!

941
01:36:31,640 --> 01:36:32,950
好地方呀，好地方呀！
It's a nice place. It's a nice place!

942
01:36:33,160 --> 01:36:33,630
对呀！
Right!

943
01:36:33,840 --> 01:36:34,550
我很累呀
I am tired!

944
01:36:34,560 --> 01:36:36,510
起码要休息三天才可以侍候你们！
I'll need at least 3 days' rest.before I can take care of you.

945
01:36:36,720 --> 01:36:38,150
没问题，三天就三天啦
No problem. As you wish.

946
01:36:39,400 --> 01:36:41,030
那为什么他们这样开心的？
Why are they so happy?

947
01:36:42,680 --> 01:36:43,550
开心！
Happy!

948
01:36:43,560 --> 01:36:46,630
我每天不能超过十个人，初一十五要吃素
No more than 10 people per day,.and I break on the 1st and 15th.

949
01:36:48,520 --> 01:36:50,710
你真的不记得那个印第安女人呀？
You really don't remember the Indian woman?

950
01:36:53,720 --> 01:36:55,550
一点印象都没有呀
No, I remember nothing!

951
01:37:01,680 --> 01:37:03,070
再见了！
See you!

952
01:37:04,080 --> 01:37:05,670
师傅，十三姨，再见了！
Master, Yee, See you

953
